title: Kunfusion
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Asian, Fusion, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Food truck turned restaurant. Vegan and gluten free items are marked on its eclectic menu which can be found in the photos section on facebook. Some vegan dishes are ep fu which is a stir-fry bowl of firm tofu, eggplant cubes, red pepper slices in a spicy hoisin sauce; and lo fu which is tempeh sauteed with onion and spices with broccoli slaw, guacamole hummus, diced cherry tomatoes. Tofu or tempeh may be subbed on some entrees. Casual lunch and dinner.
